# Games Controller Tests
# Base URL: http://localhost:5254

### Get all games (default)
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games

###

### Get games with search
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games?search=zelda

###

### Get games with pagination
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games?page=2&page_size=10

###

### Get specific game by ID (Grand Theft Auto V)
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498

###

### Get specific game by ID (The Witcher 3)
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3328

###

### Get specific game by ID (Red Dead Redemption 2)
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/28

###

### Get game screenshots
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498/screenshots

###

### Get game screenshots with pagination
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498/screenshots?page=2&page_size=5

###

### Get game DLCs/additions
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498/additions

###

### Get game stores
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498/stores

###

### Get game parent (if it's a DLC)
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498/parent

###

### Get game series
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games/3498/series

###

### Test with API Key (if enabled)
GET http://localhost:5254/api/games
X-API-Key: your-dev-key

